"""Embedded label backgrounds (generated)."""
from __future__ import annotations
import base64
from functools import lru_cache
from io import BytesIO
from reportlab.lib.utils import ImageReader

BACKGROUND_BASE64 = {
    "1.png": "",
    "2.png": "",
    "3.png": "",
}

@lru_cache(maxsize=16)
def get_background_reader(name: str) -> ImageReader:
    b64 = BACKGROUND_BASE64.get(name)
    if not b64:
        raise KeyError(f"Background not found: {name}")
    data = base64.b64decode(b64.encode("ascii"))
    return ImageReader(BytesIO(data))

def has_background(name: str) -> bool:
    return name in BACKGROUND_BASE64